reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality and Convenience.
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these because I liked the magnetic feature. I prefer things to be clean and organized in my kitchen, so I don’t have to go digging around for what I need. They’re very good quality and super convenient with them being double sided and magnetic. They are the best measuring spoons I’ve ever owned. I would 100% recommend these to anyone that loves to bake or just enjoys the esthetic of a clean kitchen drawer.

reviews.reviewText: These spoons are great. The magnets keep them neat and orderly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love these spoons
reviews.reviewText: These were a gift I gave for Christmas & my sister absolutely loves everything about them! Having both the round & oval ends to fit into different containers, the various measures, the handy leveler & that they are magnetic & easy to keep together!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wifey loves them
reviews.reviewText: Got them for a stocking stuffer for my wife. She loves that they're stronger than her old plastic ones, and have the round or oval side depending on use.Says the best part is they're magnetic so you don't have to take them off and on a ring to keep them together.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars best measuring spoon set
reviews.reviewText: These are the best! Easy to keep together but easy to separate for use. All the sizes needed, especially the smallest size (good for preparing small amounts of foods, or very potent spices). Non-staining, durable. And good price, too.

reviews.reviewText: We absolutely love these! Especially the fact that they are magnetic, however, I’m concerned about their longevity with moderate use. The larger tablespoon one is starting to bend very easily and I’m concerned it’s going to break after a little more use.
